thread.title: Bianca

author: Bianca
title: Bianca
text: Rick sold our previous property and we had no hesitation in requesting his services when it came time to sell again. He is honest, approachable and forthcoming with his opinion when required. As buyers, Rick listened to our property requirements and found us what we needed. We will certainly utilise Rick's services again should we need to buy or sell in the future.
